frames.caption: A young child dressed in traditional attire sits joyfully atop a vibrant peacock in a serene, tropical setting. The child is adorned with a golden crown and jewelry, holding a staff, while the peacock stands gracefully in a calm pond surrounded by lotus flowers. Tall palm trees and distant mountains create a tranquil backdrop under a soft, golden sky.
